Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Harery/SYSMAINT

Package: sysmaint
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.2), apt, systemd, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: fwupd, snapd
Description: Safe system maintenance script with JSON telemetry
 sysmaint is a conservative Ubuntu/Debian maintenance orchestrator that
 updates packages, trims disk usage, and emits a rich JSON summary for
 unattended operation. Features include optional final upgrade phase,
 colorized logs, log truncation safeguards, zombie process detection,
 minimal security audit, and browser cache reporting.
